          ==
        =<  win
        %-  blab:(spam tan)
        :_  ~
        :*  %pass  /kiln/[syd]  %arvo  %c
            %info
            tic  %&
            %+  murn  notations
            |=  [=path dif=(unit [=mark =vase])]
            ^-  (unit [^path miso])
